com.google.android.exoplayer.chunk

Class ChunkOperationHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer.chunk.ChunkOperationHolder

  • public final class ChunkOperationHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds a chunk operation, which consists of a either:
    • The number of MediaChunks that should be retained on the queue (queueSize) together with the next Chunk to load (chunk). chunk may be null if the next chunk cannot be provided yet.
    • A flag indicating that the end of the stream has been reached (endOfStream).
